data.description: *** PRICE ENHANCEMENT TO $319,000 PLUS $3,500 IN CLOSING COSTS**  **OWNER FNANCE OPTION NEGOTIABLE  *  ***This 2-story 4 bedroom 3 bathroom layout provides ample space for living and entertaining.**Enjoy the high ceiling in the living area and open loft upstairs, perfect for a cinema/game room.** The primary room w/ bay window and 2 bedrooms upstairs is optimal for sleeping space. One  bedroom and one full bath downstairs is convenient for a study/extra lounging area. **This home has mature oak trees, plenty of backyard space that is nicely shaded. Being equipped with solar panels makes this home energy-efficient. Having a water softener is a great asset. There is even a storage shed for your yard tools. **, beauty is conveniently located in the popular Westcreek Subdivision near Lackland Air Force Base, Wilford Hall Medical, and enjoy family fun at Sea World of Texas. Easy access to Loop 1604, 410, & Hwy 90.   *****Thank you for your interest, LET'S MAKE THIS HOME YOURS!
